comments.content:
This is [Vermin Vibes Redux](http://web.archive.org/web/20131017074447/http:/www.dafont.com/vermin-vibes-redux.font%3Cbr%20/%3E) designed by Andrew McCluskey. Dafont puts it in the "Gothic Modern" category.  
Don
